author: etnu
msg: Added www-authenticate to the disallowed response headers list to avoid a potential annoyance / spam vector where users are presented with modal dialogs when the header is present on some browsers. The proxy never handled http authentication correctly anyway, so nobody should be relying on it. makeRequest should still support this if anyone is using it.
